title: $:/litClock/times/-05:16-Ali Smith
quote_first: She could go back to sleep. But typical and ironic, she is completely awake. It is completely light outside now; you can see for miles. Except there is nothing to see here; trees and fields and that kind of thing.
quote_last: on the substandard clock radio. She is really awake.
